      "span_text": "Specifically, we used these coupling measures to reconstruct the original modularization of the software systems using a state-of-the-art tool, Bunch [CITATION_1] , and using the Move Join eFfectiveness Measure (MoJoFM) [CITATION_2] to evaluate the resulting decomposition."
